EN: The ducks in the pond are wandering around.

ZH: 池子边的柳树投下阴影。
EN: The willow tree by the pond casts a shadow.

ZH: 我的家乡有一个很美丽的池子。
EN: My hometown has a very beautiful pond.

ZH: 池子里的鱼在接受日光浴。
EN: The fish in the pond are sunbathing.

ZH: 每当我看到这个池子，就会想起童年时光。
EN: Every time I see this pond, I think of my childhood.

ZH: 池子中倒映着蓝天和白云。
EN: The pond reflects the blue sky and white clouds.

ZH: 我的奶奶喜欢在池子边上晒太阳。
